            <title>[LU-259] Wrong option in ext4-force_over_16tb-rhel6.patch</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-259</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the ext4-force_over_16tb-rhel6.patch patch we have in 2.1 tree:&lt;br/&gt;
+       &lt;/p&gt;
